                                  {Math.round(aiAnalysis.performanceAnalysis.confidenceScore * 100)}% Confidence
                                </div>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div className="mt-6 p-4 bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-700/50 rounded-lg">
                              <div className="text-blue-300 font-medium mb-2">💡 Coming Soon</div>
                              <p className="text-sm text-slate-300">
                                Enhanced scene-by-scene analysis with timestamp-based insights, 
